      <title>IPO 终于带来夏日热度，交易规模达 55 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/ipos-finally-bring-summer-heat-with-5-5-billion-in-deals-on-tap</link>
